{"type": "article", "id": 19936, "title": "飞机餐餐盘", "description": "", "date": "2015-12-30T07:20:13Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 25, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160606140500uVrdRzE2b96pNOQf.jpeg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t在飞机上吃飞机餐总有一点精神紧张，要担心食物和汤水洒到身上，或者不小心打翻水杯。这套飞机餐的设计不仅想要增加稳定性，还想要将更多的食物放在餐盘里，满足吃饱的需求。固定餐盘有 5 个缺口，就像食堂里的餐盘，能搭配“三菜一汤”。 5 个碗就卡在缺口里，也可以单独拿出来替换，即便是颠簸的时候也可以盛满食物了。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726150301wf82o0ViIXEpt1AL.jpg\" width=\"1050\" height=\"875\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.83333333\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201607261503012UYMbNpRKnLg1aiX.jpg\" width=\"1050\" height=\"691\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.65809524\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<div>\r\n</div>\n\n\n\n"}